Products.RichDescription:
Helga's Gluten Free Bread 5 Seeds for the 'real bread' experience

Introducing Helga's New gluten free bread - it's full of all the good things you love about Helga's, without the gluten.

Helga's bakers have transformed our gluten free recipe to bake loaves with bigger slices so that you can enjoy satisfying sandwiches and toast everyday.

Every slice is soft and delicious so sandwiches are back on the menu!

So whether you're craving a chicken and salad sandwich or scrumptious honey toast, New Helga's gluten free bread means you can finally enjoy bread again.

It's not just bread it's Helga's.

- Source of fibre.

- No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

- Baked in Australia.
